data.description: Welcome to ur dream home! This exquisite 5 bdrm 4 bath Jeff Benton masterpiece is nestled in coveted River Park community, offering the perfect blend of luxury & comfort. W/ prime location across from the pool, relaxation & entertainment are at ur fingertips. Crafted w/ impeccable attention to detail, this full brick home boasts a stunning stone exterior that exudes elegance. 3-car garage provides ample space for vehicles & storage, while the spacious eat-in kitchen is a chef's delight, feat modern appliances & abundant countertop space for culinary creations. Indulge in leisure & play in the generous rec room. The dedicated office provides the privacy u seek, ensuring productivity & focus.
